          <head>
            <note type="contents-note">This manuscript contains: The first volume of a collection of Anthems, Chants, and Prayers, for the festivals of the whole year, according to the use of the Maronites of Mount Lebanon. In total, including sub-sections, this manuscript contains 5 items.</note>
            <listRelation type="Wright-BL-Taxonomy">
